# FlowDesk

> Run your business from one dashboard.

---

# Project Overview

FlowDesk is a modern Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) platform designed to simplify the day-to-day operations of service-based businesses. It provides an all-in-one solution for managing customers, employees, services, bookings, reports, and business operations through a single, intuitive dashboard.

Rather than relying on multiple applications, spreadsheets, paper records, and messaging platforms, FlowDesk centralizes essential business functions into one secure cloud-based platform that can be accessed from anywhere.

The project is being developed as a full-stack web application and serves as both a professional portfolio project and the foundation for a commercial software product.

---

# Problem Statement

Many small and medium-sized service businesses still rely on disconnected tools such as notebooks, spreadsheets, messaging apps, calendars, and paper records to manage their daily operations.

This often leads to:

- Missed appointments
- Double bookings
- Poor customer management
- Lost business information
- Inefficient staff coordination
- Limited reporting and business insights

Existing solutions are often designed for a single industry, include unnecessary complexity, or require expensive subscriptions that are not practical for growing businesses.

FlowDesk aims to solve these challenges by providing an affordable, flexible, and user-friendly platform that adapts to different service-based businesses.

